title: At World's Trend 9/8: Odell Beckham Jr, Travis Scott, Trump Boaters, Peloton, Xbox Series S
itunes:title: At World's Trend 9/8: Odell Beckham Jr, Travis Scott, Trump Boaters, Peloton, Xbox Series S
description:
On this edition of Pirates of the Carribean 3: At World's Trend Jack and Miles discuss rumors about ODB's sexual interests, Travis Scott launched a meal deal collab with McDonald's, a boat-based Trump rally lead to quite a few sunk vessels, Peloton announces a Treadmill and a 2nd edition Bike, and Microsoft announces the slightly cheaper Xbox Series S coming out in November.
